item.title: My first post
item.description: Hello everyone! My name is Zachary Bensley and I’m a full stack web developer. Thanks for reading my first blog posting. Sorry, it’s just an intro post. I’ll do my best to have a real post soon. I’m planning to use this blog to share my ideas and discuss current projects.
